cast.overview: When three friends finally come to after a raucous night of bachelor-party revelry, they find a baby in the closet and a tiger in the bathroom. But they can't seem to locate their best friend, Doug – who's supposed to be tying the knot. Launching a frantic search for Doug, the trio perseveres through a nasty hangover to try to make it to the church on time.
cast.title: The Hangover

cast.overview: A family discovers that dark spirits have invaded their home after their son inexplicably falls into an endless sleep. When they reach out to a professional for help, they learn things are a lot more personal than they thought.
cast.title: Insidious

details.biography: Andrew Astor was born in Arizona. The Astor family bloodline dates back to 1623 on his father's side and while the Astor family are most notably relatives of the English & German John Jacob Astor family, that bloodline also includes decedents from Northern Italy and Spain. Andrew's mother is Sicilian and grew up in the Bronx surrounded by members of "the family".
details.name: Andrew Astor
